review_blob: As you might guess, this is a perfect beer for a warm summer day.  The lemon flavor comes through well, and it is overall a very nice and refreshing beer.
Excellent IPA.  Dogfish is brewed about 15 minutes from where I live, so that is awesome.  Represent.  As for the beer itself, it is definitely quite hoppy and the citrus comes through splendidly.
Great seasonal beer.  Nice warm amber color.  Really makes me wish it was October right now.
